<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=euc-kr" />
    <title>05_가입전알릴사항</title>
    <!--<link rel="shortcut icon" href="https://direct.hi.co.kr/images/common/favicon.ico"/>-->
    <script language="JavaScript" src="../../js/lib/jquery-1.11.2.min.js"></script>
    <script language="JavaScript" src="../../js/lib/jquery-ui.min.js"></script>
    <script language="JavaScript" src="../../js/lib/jquery-fakeform-0.5.js"></script>
    <script language="JavaScript" src="../../js/common.js"></script>

    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"  href="../../css/jquery-ui.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"  href="../../css/base.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"  href="../../css/common.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"  href="../../css/layout.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"  href="../../css/content.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"  href="../../css/popup.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"  href="../../css/overseas_trip.css" />
</head>
<body class="boxType">
<!--skipNavi : s-->
<ul class="skipNavi">
    <li><a href="#contents">본문바로가기</a></li>
</ul>
<!--skipNavi : e-->
<div class="contentWrap">
    <!--leftArea : s-->
    <div class="leftArea">
        <div class="topBox">
            <p class="logo"><a href="#"><img src="https://direct.hi.co.kr/images/common/logo_small.png" alt="형대해상 다이렉트"></a></p>
            <h1>국내여행보험</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="stepArea">
        </div>
        <div class="bottomBtn bottomFixed">
            <div class="btnArea">
                <a href="#" class="btnHelp">도움말</a>
                <a href="#" class="btnNew">최근계산내역</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!--leftArea : e-->
    <!--contentArea : s -->
    <div class="contentArea" id="contents">
        <!--titleArea : s-->
        <div class="topTitleArea">
            <h2>가입 전 알릴사항</h2>
            <p class="txt">[예] 또는 [아니오]를 선택해주세요. [예] 선택 시 보험 가입이 제한될 수 있습니다.</p>
        </div>
        <!--titleArea : e-->

        <!--confirmTable : s-->
        <div class="confirmTable noAllSet">
            <div class="topTitle">
                <div class="rightArea">
                    <div class="checkbox checkAll">
                        <input type="checkbox" id="noAll">
                        <label for="noAll">모두 아니오</label>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <ol class="confirmList">
                <li>
                    <div class="titleWrap">
                        <div class="title line2">
                            <div class="num">1.</div>
                            <div class="txt">최근 5년 이내에 암, 백혈병, 협심증, 심근경색, 심장판막증, 간경화, 뇌졸증,<br> 뇌출혈, 에이즈 질병으로 진단/치료를 받은 적이 있습니까?</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="rightArea">
                            <div class="confirm dataSelect">
                                <ul>
                                    <li><a href="#" class="yes" data-media-value="yes">예</a></li>
                                    <li><a href="#" class="no" data-media-value="no">아니오</a></li>
                                </ul>
                                <input type="hidden" id="confirm1">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </li>               
                <li>
                    <div class="titleWrap">
                        <div class="title">
                            <div class="num">2.</div>
                            <div class="txt">유전성 질환을 갖고 계십니까?</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="rightArea">
                            <div class="confirm dataSelect">
                                <ul>
                                    <li><a href="#" class="yes" data-media-value="yes">예</a></li>
                                    <li><a href="#" class="no" data-media-value="no">아니오</a></li>
                                </ul>
                                <input type="hidden" id="confirm4">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </li>
            </ol>
        </div>
        <!--confirmTable : e-->

   
        <!--alertInfo : s-->
        <div class="alertInfo">
            <p class="title">유의사항</p>
            <div class="conArea">
                <ul class="listStyle dot">
                    <li>보험가입에 필요한 알릴 사항을 사실대로 선택해주세요.</li>
                    <li>알릴 의무를 위반하는 경우 보험금의 지급이 거절될 수 있으며 보험계약이 해지될 수 있습니다.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!--alertInfo : e-->


        <!--btnAreaWrap : s-->
        <div class="btnAreaWrap txtBtn">           
            <div class="btnArea">
                <a href="#" class="btn small mail"><span>이메일/문자로 받기</span></a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!--btnAreaWrap : e-->


        <div class="bottomFixed">
            <div class="btnAreaWrap">
                <ul class="btnArea item37">
                    <li><a href="#" class="btn prev"><span>이전</span></a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" class="btn next"><span>다음</span></a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="btnClose"><img src="https://direct.hi.co.kr/images/common/btn_close.png" alt="닫기"></a>
    </div>
    <!--contentArea : e -->
</div>
</body>
</html>